 female members simply do a better job of representing their constituents than male members.  aDescription based on information from the publisher. 0aWomen in public life. 0aWomen public officers. 0aSex discrimination against women. 4aElectronic books.1 aSteigerwalt, Amy,d1976-eauthor.22aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)eissuing body,epublisher. 0aLegislative politics & policy making.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.9718595